Package: agconversions
Type: Package
Title: Converting agricultural statistics from imperial to metric
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Gurneet", "Braich", email = "g.braich@mail.ubc.ca",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Gurneet Braich <g.braich@mail.ubc.ca>
Description: A tool for converting between units for agriculture data. As
    agriculture is a global activity, the measurements of common agriculture
    variables such as temperature, area, weight and volumes can diverse. This
    package uses conversion ratios to convert traditional measurements such as
    acres, Fahrenheit, pounds etc. to SI/metric units.
